Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Kenta Ochiai, a typical college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately l've scored with seven different women!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some might say it's just because of Suwatee's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's more to it than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about me makes girls crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a bad boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've had this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this girl! And this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mine! Mine! Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets lucky for the first time in his life and he goes crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! l can't believe you're running around in this heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning to freeload off me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here two weeks already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you think, Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all having so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's too hot! Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Saiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l need to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not something weird, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a sweet deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't keep my resort hotel job anymore. Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get three meals a day, and there are gorgeous girls everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only man in a harem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l can get laid every day all summer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l've got a woody just thinking about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else who can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't say no when my buddy asks for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem a little too excited to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Then, l'll tag along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! l'm not going for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taitei! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this any way to treat your brand new wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know that you used the power of the star to have sex with that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree! So you really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew how l felt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like l said, it never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be embarrassed, Shuree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l still remember how you cried and confessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Kenta, don't forget about me!''
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way l would say such a stupid thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am taking away your powers as a goddess for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, the same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your punishment, you will both spend a little time as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How appetizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous girls everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! Slow down and stop drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President Hotel, President Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart! Come stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have good rooms! How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, are you looking for a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no... You're Sanada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Kenta Ochiai, the new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came! l've been waiting, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to work part time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's pretty last-minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mr. Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're that desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! l'll find something for both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, put your stuff in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's beautiful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this the hotel limo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so glad l'm alive! Girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that one! Ours is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki, you bastard! You lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l give up now, l won't be able to accomplish my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, where are you from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sanada, this hotel is really quiet. Where are the customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old miser named Arisugawa put up that huge luxury hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and stole all my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My business is non-existent, thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sweetie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go for a swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! No luck at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never score without our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a midget, you stupid mortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he crazy from the heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lce cold juice! Beer! lnner tubes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lce cold juice! Beer! lnner tubes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also give oil massages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Sanada, this is the Sunday Hotel's private beach, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it. lf we get caught, then we get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So our ''regular'' customer is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lce cold juice! Beer! lnner tubes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Kenta! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada, you again? Don't you ever learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she knows you, Mr. Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hey, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're security for Sunday Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Amazon Gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Miyuki Himuro. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee, what do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuit, a swimsuit. We're at the beach, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get me this swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! But we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and change too, Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta might fall for you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to at least give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No charge for the towing service!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right, Suwatee! Have some confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so cute, Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Welcome to the grand opening of our beach bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a drink with Shuree and Suwatee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Suwatee... Business! Business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What would you like to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, little boys, if you don't behave, l'll close the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mahoko, you're that old miser's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l mean, the president's granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, you guys have a lot of guts to compete against my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so eccentric and stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and l'm totally bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes l sneak out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now l'll be on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'd be great if a cute girl like you were helping us, Mahoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems rather lively in front of Sanada's hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received information that he has hired three part-time workers for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought l would run him off this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, is Mahoko back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she hasn't returned from the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surfing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all she does, morning to night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? And who was it that first interested her in surfing, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely what you would call pennies from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee and Shuree have saved this hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be the Goddesses of Luck come down to Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Mr. Sanada! How did you guess our true identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ldiot! Shuree, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, this is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been a while since l've had so much fun! Look, l'm dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}l'm a really good dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, were you hitting on some girl this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}See! Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you score?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a cheap drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}l'm Sanada the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, maybe you wanna have a go at it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Samurai Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Samurai Sanada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what you promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief! A drunken goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so sweet when she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lt felt so familiar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you adjusting to life as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's probably harder than life in heaven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l always wished l could feel the wind and water like you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm happy that l get to be by your side, like a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get to the store before it closes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah! l know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that always happen when it's about to get good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't be too pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she has a real body now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee is still a goddess, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know, this is all very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, baby? Too scared to stick up for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Keep your filthy hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spoiled brat! You making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big hotel of yours is killing our business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you need to get off your butts and work a little harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four guys against one girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really never learns, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real-life controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that time playing video games wasn't a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm okay. Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot. You really bailed me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's smarter to just run, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l shouldn't have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're feisty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to ignore your activities on the beach because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what l'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But l can give you a little ''thank you''.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're so wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... l haven't gotten any in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good! lt's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think l'm going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either! l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.25,0:24:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.19,0:24:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.99,0:25:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your English teacher comes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just out for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell such transparent lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.10,0:25:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting suspicious all summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.40,0:25:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're grounded! No more games!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.31,0:25:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko, someday you will take over the management of this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to behave like a young lady so that you can find a husband to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's my marriage so l'll find my own husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.39,0:25:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my life, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.43,0:25:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets worse every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.38,0:25:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.32,0:26:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good, l take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.16,0:26:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before that idiot falls for another woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.43,0:26:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.83,0:26:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls there a Kenta Ochiai here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.17,0:26:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Kenta's?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.41,0:26:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.88,0:26:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l came to work with you guys, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.82,0:26:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.32,0:26:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work with us? But it's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.53,0:26:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.33,0:26:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please? Please? Kenta, please! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.38,0:27:08.51,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sagashi tsuzuketeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.38,0:27:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have the one bright smile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:16.02,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kagayaku sono egao{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that l've always been looking for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:21.69,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yume ni made miteta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These arms of yours that hold me tight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.27,0:27:28.90,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dakishimeru sono tewo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.27,0:27:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...l have only dreamed about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.94,0:27:35.14,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Subetewa hajimatte ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.94,0:27:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l remember when it started...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:43.95,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}deatta shunkan ni kizuita yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the day l saw you standing there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:47.19,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kono sora no hate ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stretch our wings to the sky,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.19,0:27:52.63,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tsubasa hiroge FLYAWAY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.19,0:27:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}take wing, and then we fly away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:57.13,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futari tobitatouyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soaring off together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.13,0:28:00.44,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eien he tsuzuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.13,0:28:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We share an endless love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:04.51,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}owaranaimo LOVE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that lasts for eternity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.51,0:28:10.15,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futari nara, ame no yoru mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.51,0:28:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two together through the rain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.15,0:28:17.09,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}samui asa mo mitsukerareru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.15,0:28:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...through the cold, holding each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:19.29,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still the moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still the moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.29,0:28:28.46,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}eien he tsuzuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.29,0:28:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...from here to eternity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.55,0:28:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT TlME
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.09,0:28:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with that girl, Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.56,0:28:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Kenta seem awfully friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.29,0:28:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.06,0:28:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know! Why don't you just give up on Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.60,0:29:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not now that l can finally touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.97,0:29:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean with a real body, you can do this and that with him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Shuree! Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.27,0:29:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Can Can Bunny Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.84,0:29:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, how do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.01,0:29:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
